data.description: Get ready for Intracoastal living with this 4 bedroom, raised beach house directly across the street from the ICW. When you arrive, you will notice the tremendous curb appeal and welcoming front porch with plenty of parking for your guests. Upon entering, you will see natural light pouring in through an abundance of windows, hardwood flooring and double crown molding throughout. The kitchen has bright white cabinets, with plenty of counter (Corian) space, recessed lighting, pantry and a raised breakfast bar. Master suite is located on the main level, and features access to the balcony. Master bath has a double vanity, whirlpool tub, and separate shower.  Upstairs, you will find 3 additional bedrooms including a 2nd master suite and plenty of closet and storage space. The 2 additional bedrooms share a jack and jill bathroom. There is also a loft sitting area. Ground level includes 2 garage bays, with parking for 3 cars - a workshop, hobby area and half bath. Perfect for entertaining, the yard is fenced and has an outside wood burning fireplace on the covered balcony - perfect for those cooler nights. This home features dual HVAC units replaced in 2015 and 2017 and 2 hot water heaters - replaced in 2013 and 2019. The property also includes your own personal boat dock and ramp - so you can enjoy all the waterway has to offer! Additionally, the location is convenient to plenty of shopping, dining, and entertainment options, and just a short drive to the beach.  Measurements are not guaranteed and are the buyer's responsibility to verify.
